---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '@components/ui/Button.astro';
import Divider from '@components/ui/Divider.astro';
import { SITE, SOCIALS } from '@lib/constants';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn the story behind Faithfully Crafted — Faith's journey from hobby crocheter to handmade artisan in the Philippines."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <header class="pt-12 sm:pt-16 pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-700 text-text" data-reveal="up">
        About <span class="font-brand text-primary-bold">{SITE.crafter}</span>
      </h1>
      <p
        class="mt-4 text-text-muted text-lg max-w-lg mx-auto"
        data-reveal="up"
        data-reveal-delay="100"
      >
        The heart and hands behind every stitch
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <article class="pb-16 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 group perspective-1000" data-reveal="left">
          <div class="relative w-64 sm:w-80 mx-auto">
            <!-- Decorative background layers -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 rounded-3xl translate-x-3 translate-y-3 sm:translate-x-4 sm:translate-y-4 -rotate-3 transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-5 group-hover:translate-y-6 group-hover:-rotate-6 shadow-sm"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-lavender/30 rounded-3xl -translate-x-2 -translate-y-2 sm:-translate-x-3 sm:-translate-y-3 rotate-2 transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover:-translate-x-4 group-hover:-translate-y-5 group-hover:rotate-4 shadow-sm"></div>
            
            <!-- Main Photo Frame -->
            <div class="relative w-full bg-body p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-primary/10 rotate-[-1deg] transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 border border-surface flex flex-col z-10 box-border bg-white">
              <!-- Washi Tape piece -->
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-20 h-5 bg-white/70 border border-white/40 shadow-sm -rotate-2 z-20 backdrop-blur-md opacity-90" style="clip-path: polygon(2% 10%, 98% 0%, 100% 90%, 0% 100%);"></div>

              <div class="relative aspect-square sm:aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-surface shadow-inner">
                <img
                  src="/faith.jpg"
                  alt="Faith, the crafter behind Faithfully Crafted"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 ease-out group-hover:scale-105"
                  loading="eager"
                />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-black/5 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none mix-blend-overlay"></div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Frame Caption -->
              <div class="pt-4 pb-2 text-center pointer-events-none">
                <span class="font-brand text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-primary-bold/90 drop-shadow-sm">The face behind the craft</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Story -->
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-5" data-reveal="right">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-700 text-text">My Story</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            It all started with a gift — a set of crochet hooks from my boyfriend, because I kept
            asking for them. I wanted to try something new, and he believed in me enough to say "go
            for it." My very first creation was a little bee, and I remember being so proud of it,
            showing it to my friends, my mom, and my brothers.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            What began as a spontaneous hobby quickly grew into something more. Friends started
            pushing me to sell my pieces, even though I was still a beginner. I thought about it,
            took a deep breath, and went for it — and
            <strong class="text-text">Faithfully Crafted</strong> was born. The name carries a special
            meaning: "Faith" is my name, and everything I make is crafted
            <em>faithfully</em>, with love and care in every single stitch.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            I wouldn't be here without my family. My mom buys yarn whenever I need it, my brothers
            got me stands and hooks without ever being asked twice — just pure support, no
            questions, nothing expected in return. And my boyfriend, who started all of this with
            that first gift, has been my biggest cheerleader from day one.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Faithfully Crafted celebrated its first anniversary in December 2025, and I still can't
            believe how far this little hobby has come. Based in {SITE.location}, I work from my
            crafting corner turning colorful yarn into amigurumi, keychains, accessories, and custom
            gifts that bring smiles. I believe handmade creations carry something special — a warmth
            and love that you just can't find anywhere else.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <Divider class="my-12" />

      <!-- Process Section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="0">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-bold"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-700 text-lg text-text">Imagine</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-muted text-sm">
            Every piece starts with an idea — whether it's your vision or mine, we dream it up
            together.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="150">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-2xl bg-lavender/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-lavender"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-700 text-lg text-text">Create</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-muted text-sm">
            Hook in hand, I bring it to life stitch by stitch — with patience, love, and the perfect
            yarn.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="300">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-2xl bg-mint/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-mint"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 8v13m0-13V6a2 2 0 112 2h-2zm0 0V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 109.5 8H12zm-7 4h14M5 12a2 2 0 110-4h14a2 2 0 110 4M5 12v7a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-7"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-700 text-lg text-text">Deliver</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-muted text-sm">
            Wrapped with care and ready to bring joy — your handmade treasure, delivered to your
            doorstep.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <Divider class="my-12" />

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center" data-reveal="scale">
        <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-6">Want something made just for you?</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <Button href={SOCIALS.facebook.messenger} variant="primary" size="lg" external>
            Let's create together
          </Button>
          <Button href="/gallery/" variant="secondary" size="lg"> Browse my work </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
